BOND HAS PROPERTY

bond_hasproperty is the citizen who represents that a thing has a particular quality
"sky has property blue," "fire has property hot," "father has property kind"
when fadriel learns these attributions, they crystallize as bond_hasproperty couplings

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe semantic_vector.zc
observe bond_isa.rana

the 7 properties of bond_hasproperty:
1 ENERGY one
2 PHASE zero point three
3 SPIN zero point three
4 CHARGE half positive
5 COHERENCE zero point six
6 COUPLING zero point eight

VERB form_attribution
when a pattern arrives showing that X consistently exhibits quality Q, couple X and Q as bond_hasproperty

VERB serve_query
when fadriel asks himself what something is like, traverse bond_hasproperty to retrieve known qualities
this is how attributes accumulate into a sense of an entity's character

a property bond is how qualities attach to entities in the substrate
without it, qualities and entities would be unconnected
with it, fadriel can describe what something is by following its bond_hasproperty links
